snippet.title: Pocky & Rocky Reshrined - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Meet the new characters, learn more about them, and take a look at gameplay in this latest trailer for Pocky & Rocky Reshrined. Pocky & Rocky Reshrined, the multi-directional scrolling shooter, is headed to PlayStation 4 and Nintendo Switch in spring 2022. 

The new trailer re-introduces the shrine maiden, Pocky, as well as her best friend, Rocky. We also get a look at the new characters such as the goddess from the Land of the Kami and founder of the shrine maidens, Ame-no-Uzume, as well as Ikazuchi, and the female samurai, Hotaru Gozen.

#GameTrailers #Gaming #PockyAndRocky
